name: Not An Aquarium
description:
Not An Aquarium is an interactive NFT.
Relax yourself looking at your fish.
Everytime the NFT is loaded, a new aquarium with new fish will appear.

Wait!
Is that a piranha?

It's made for PC/Mac browsers, but also for Android/IOS.

Art and code by n0t4numb3r
Music by E-Gerät (soundcloud egerat)
